summary: Do any of you have special abilities like Psychic powers or aura?
question: Do any of you have special abilities like Psychic powers or aura?
answer:
Riku: Having a bond as strong as he does with a psychic pokemon, there’s bound to be some things that rub off…

Not that I don’t love seeing you two make googly eyes at each other all night, but can you use that psychic link of yours to figure out when Sora will be back? It’s been over an hour.

Hare: Espee….

Riku: -sigh- I’ll just wait here, I guess. /Where does he always go off to…?/

summary: A brain region for Pokémon characters? The findings, published online in the journal Nature Human Behavior, help shed light on...
caption:
A brain region for Pokémon characters?

The findings, published online in the journal Nature Human Behavior, help shed light on two related mysteries about our visual system. “It’s been an open question in the field why we have brain regions that respond to words and faces but not to, say, cars,” said study first author and former Stanford graduate student Jesse Gomez. “It’s also been a mystery why they appear in the same place in everyone’s brain.”
